  "title": "Quantity Surveyor",
  "description": "<p>Job Description</p><p>-         \nTabulate quantities, estimate cost and request\nfor quotation</p><p>-         \nGeneral Contract administration and measurement\nworks</p><p>-         \nLiaise with subcontractor and clients</p><p>-         \nEnsure timely completion of an assign tender</p><p>-         \nUpdating contract documents, drawings, and\ncorrespondences</p><p>-         \nOther quantity surveyor duties as assigned</p><p>-         \nBetter to have final account experience </p><p>Job Requirements</p><p>-         \nMinimum Diploma in Quantity Surveying or\nequivalent</p><p>-         \nMinimum 2-year experience in residential housing\npreferred and final account work</p><p>-         \nProficient in MS Office and other Measurement\nSoftware</p><p>-         \nShows independency ability to multi-task,\nprioritize, and organise tasks</p><p>-         \nAbility to liaise with consultants, subcons and\nclient</p><p>-         \nFamiliar with VOs, Als, EOT and final account\nwork</p>",
